longBusinessSummary: Fortitude Gold Corporation, a mining company, focuses on exploring for gold projects. It also explores for silver deposits. The company's flagship property is the Isabella Pearl mine project covering an area of approximately 9,000 acres located in the Mineral County, Nevada. The company was incorporated in 2020 and is headquartered in Colorado Springs, Colorado.
